text: Ramjan Ali is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Meherpur-1. ==Career== Ali was elected to parliament from Meherpur-1 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Ramjan Ali
